#

Pumpkin Seed Granola

35 min
$5.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VeganNut-FreeGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastSnackHealthyEasy

Description

Crunchy and nutritious, this pumpkin seed granola is perfect for breakfast or a snack!

Ingredients

  • rolled oats: 2 cups
  • pumpkin seeds: 1 cup
  • honey or maple syrup: 1/3 cup
  • coconut oil: 1/4 cup
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • cinnamon: 1 tsp
